  "elapsed_s": 16.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Like we were marching, I remember, to the laundry, and the two SS men which were with us were especially stupid people from Romania, originally.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were ordered to sing while we are marching.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We are marching like a herd of cattle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, after you are some remnants of men, march!",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sing!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Singing didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So somebody got beaten and they said-- they said to me, can you do something at least?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, maybe we can whistle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So, OK, whistle.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we are trying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we started to whistle, like one man, 'It's a Long Way to Tipperary.' And the British prisoners and the American prisoners were running towards the street looking and we were totally crazy.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they saw these-- these 100 prisoners simply walking to the laundry room whistling 'It's a Long Way to Tipperary.' That's how we got their attention.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
